<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٠٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هي <span class="c2">(أمته)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> يصنع بها ما شاء.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
